```python
        for htype, pt in corners.items():
```
# 遍历四角手柄字典：`htype` 手柄类型、`pt` 对应角点坐标

```python
            if abs(pos.x() - pt.x()) < hs and abs(pos.y() - pt.y()) < hs:
```
# 条件判断：abs(pos.x() - pt.x()) < hs and abs(pos.y() - pt.y()) < hs

```python
                return htype
```
# 返回 htype

```python
        for htype, pt in edges.items():
```
# 遍历四边中点手柄字典：角手柄未命中时继续检测边手柄

```python
            if abs(pos.x() - pt.x()) < hs and abs(pos.y() - pt.y()) < hs:
```
# 条件判断：abs(pos.x() - pt.x()) < hs and abs(pos.y() - pt.y()) < hs

```python
                return htype
```
# 返回 htype

