```
# 跳过当前循环迭代，继续下一个

```python
                anchor_idx = item.get_anchor_at(pos.x(), pos.y(), PenTool.ANCHOR_TOLERANCE)
```
# 调用 item.get_anchor_at() 并将结果赋给 anchor_idx

```python
                if anchor_idx >= 0 and item.anchor_count > 2:
```
# 条件判断：anchor_idx >= 0 and item.anchor_count > 2

```python
                    old_anchors = [a.copy() for a in item.anchors]
```
# 调用 [a.copy() 并将结果赋给 old_anchors

```python
                    item.remove_anchor(anchor_idx)
```
# 调用 item.remove_anchor() 函数

```python
                    new_anchors = [a.copy() for a in item.anchors]
```
# 调用 [a.copy() 并将结果赋给 new_anchors

```python
                    cmd = ModifyAnchorCommand(doc, item, old_anchors, new_anchors)
```
# 调用 ModifyAnchorCommand() 并将结果赋给 cmd

```python
                    doc.execute_command(cmd)
```
# 调用 doc.execute_command() 函数

```python
                    return
```
# 提前返回，不再继续后续检测

